│ `TryToMergeBlockIntoPredecessor`, which is called by `simplifycfg`. However, the block     │
│ `bb1` is not actually folded because it has two successors (`bb3` and `panic1`). The debug │
│ message is printed before the check that aborts the merge.                                 │
